SECTION 2: MANDATORY ATTRIBUTION CONDITIONS

These conditions apply to ALL users (both Free and Commercial Tiers).
Attribution is NON-NEGOTIABLE and must be maintained at all times.

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.1 SOURCE CODE ATTRIBUTION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Every source code file MUST retain the original copyright notice at the top:

/*
 * E-Commerce Storefront
 * Original creator: Himanshu
 * GitHub: https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu
 * License: Dual-License (Community / Commercial) v2.0
 *
 * [Your modifications below this line]
*/

You MAY NOT:
  ✗ Remove or comment-out the original copyright header
  ✗ Replace the original author name
  ✗ Hide the GitHub link
  ✗ Modify the license reference

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.2 PROJECT DOCUMENTATION ATTRIBUTION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Your README.md MUST include an "Attribution" or "Credits" section with:

## Attribution

Built on **E-Commerce Storefront** by [Himanshu](https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu)

[View License](./LICENSE)

REQUIREMENTS:
  ✓ Visible without expanding collapsed sections
  ✓ Active hyperlinks that work
  ✓ Appears in primary README (not in secondary docs only)
  ✓ Cannot be paraphrased or summarized

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.3 DEPLOYED APPLICATION FOOTER ATTRIBUTION
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you deploy a live storefront, every page MUST include visible footer credit:

"Powered by E-Commerce Software | [Link to GitHub]"

LEGIBILITY REQUIREMENTS (STRICTLY ENFORCED):
  ✓ Font size: minimum 11px
  ✓ Color contrast: minimum 4.5:1 ratio against background
  ✓ Fully visible (no hiding, no tricks)

PROHIBITED TECHNIQUES (VIOLATIONS):
  ✗ display: none, visibility: hidden, opacity < 0.8
  ✗ position: absolute/fixed with off-screen coordinates
  ✗ z-index layering behind other elements
  ✗ Color matching text to background
  ✗ Font size below threshold

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2.4 COMPONENT & IMPORT TRACKING
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you substantially use or fork components from this Software, document them.
Include comments in the code identifying the original source:

// Based on E-Commerce Software component
// Original: https://github.com/Newbie-Himanshu

