QUICK DECISION TREE

Do you charge customers money or generate revenue using this software?
    YES → You MUST have a Commercial License
    NO  → Can you use the Free Tier?

Are you a registered business entity (company, LLC, Partnership, GSTIN)?
    YES (even if not using for this project) → You likely need Commercial License
    NO  → Free Tier might apply

Are you an approved non-profit with registered status?
    YES → Free Tier (with attribution)
    NO  → See revenue question above

